{"ProductId":"330","Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Elements","ShortDescription":"Textured overlays paired with clean, square edges and durable insulated steel gives you the look of painted wood without the upkeep","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/crelementsshowcase-emilyhenderson.webp?sfvrsn=a9a42851_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/elements","Overview":"<h3>Reliable Performance, Stunning Style</h3><h4>Rugged 4-Layer Construction</h4><p>Built with a tough steel interior and exterior, high-performance insulation, and a composite overlay for a wood-look finish that lasts.</p><h4>Woodgrain Appeal, Zero Hassle</h4><p>The composite overlay is carefully molded with a realistic woodgrain texture, so you get the classic style of painted wood&mdash;without the ongoing maintenance.</p><h4>Make It Yours</h4><p>Pick from 13 different designs, add optional windows or decorative hardware, and choose from 7 standard paint colors&mdash;or over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">custom Color Blast&reg; options</a>.</p><h4>Comfort and Efficiency</h4><p>The 1-3/8&rdquo; polystyrene insulation (R-value 6.5) helps keep your garage comfortable and energy-efficient, no matter the season.</p><h4>Built for Tough Conditions</h4><p>For homes in high-wind areas, <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; door reinforcement</a> is available for extra peace of mind.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Built for Strength and Lasting Performance</h3><p>Canyon Ridge&reg; Elements garage doors are engineered to handle life&rsquo;s demands, inside and out. Each door starts with a heavy-duty steel base for strength and stability. On top of that is a layer of thick polystyrene insulation which helps to keep your garage quiet, energy-efficient, and comfortable in every season. The exterior gets a second layer of steel, then a moisture-resistant composite overlay that looks just like painted wood, but won&rsquo;t rot, warp or crack.</p><p>To keep your door looking and working its best, the steel skins are finished with a multi-step rust-prevention system: hot-dipped galvanizing, a protective metal oxide treatment, and a baked-on primer and topcoat for long-lasting durability. The bottom of the door features a replaceable vinyl weather seal set in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer to keep out air and water. For peace of mind, the patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; helps prevent accidental injuries, and removable window grilles make cleaning simple.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-canyon-ridge-elements-4l.webp?sfvrsn=2a15a388_4\" alt=\"Canyon Ridge Elements\" sf-size=\"100\" /><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Composite Overlay</li><li>Steel</li><li>Polystyrene Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Canyon Ridge Elements","DisplayIndex":1,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/canyon-ridge-elements","ColorDisclaimer":"<p><strong><em></em></strong>With Canyon Ridge&reg; Elements, you can pick from a curated palette of classic and contemporary colors to perfectly complement your home. Standard options include crisp White, rich Bronze, deep Charcoal, bold Black, warm Desert Tan, and striking Iron Ore. Each finish is carefully selected to highlight the door&rsquo;s wood-look texture and clean lines, adding instant curb appeal.</p><p>Want something a little different? The two-tone option lets you mix and match&mdash;choose one color for the steel base and another for the composite overlay for a truly custom look. If you have a specific shade in mind, the Color Blast&reg; program opens up over 1,500 custom colors, making it easy to match your garage door to your front door, trim, or any other detail on your home.<em></em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>Canyon Ridge® Elements gives you plenty of ways to personalize the top section of your garage door, blending privacy, natural light, and architectural flair.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nFor a classic, seamless look, Series 1 and 2 Solid top sections (TOP11, TOP12, TOP13, and ARCH1) keep things simple and refined—perfect for homeowners who want a clean, understated style.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nIf you’d like to invite in more light or add a decorative touch, you can choose from a wide range of window designs. Options like REC11, REC13, REC14, SQ23, SQ24, and several arched styles (ARCH1, ARCH3, ARCH4, ARCH13, ARCH14) let you pick the shape and pattern that best suits your home. These windows not only brighten your garage but also give your door a distinctive, welcoming appearance.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\nFor double doors, special designs like ARC1A, ARC3A, ARC4A, ARC13A, and ARC14A are available in both solid and windowed versions, ensuring a balanced, beautiful look no matter the size of your opening.</p>\r\n","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Every Canyon Ridge® Elements door comes standard with spade lift handles—sturdy, easy to grip, and designed for the door’s carriage house style. If you want to personalize further, you can upgrade to other handle designs like spear or colonial lift handles or opt for decorative styles such as the ring door knocker, escutcheon plates, or twisted “L” handles. Each handle is crafted from durable materials for long-lasting use and a satisfying feel.</p>\r\n<p>Step plates and hinges let you fine-tune the details: choose from spade, spear, or colonial styles to match your handles or create your own combination. All hardware is finished in a weather-resistant black powder coat, giving you a timeless look that won’t fade or chip easily.</p>\r\n","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-canyonridgebr-20-1.webp?sfvrsn=9c9dfc36_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-CANYONRIDGEBR-20.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Manual for Residential Sectional Insulated Steel Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-insulatedresi.webp?sfvrsn=15f3a601_3","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150077_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Care and Maintenance","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/care-and-maintenance/cmb-4150084_en.webp?sfvrsn=d710b9a2_2","Type":"Finish & Care","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CMB-4150084_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Installation Warranty","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/warranty/cbpc-madadgdinstallwarranty1yr-15.webp?sfvrsn=99c1bfdc_4","Type":"Warranty","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CBPC-MADADGDINSTALLWARRANTY1YR-15.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":3},{"Title":"Instructions for Shimming Overlay Door","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/sup-0137441_en.webp?sfvrsn=8eac8dbd_1","Type":"Installation and Maintenance","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/SUP-0137441_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":4}],"ProductImageGallery":[{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/normal/emilyhenderson-garagedoors_kaitlingreenl.webp?sfvrsn=2d29beb0_1","ThumbnailImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/thumbnails/emilyhenderson-garagedoors_kaitlingreens.webp?sfvrsn=dba5721c_1","VideoUrl":null,"Title":"Canyon Ridge Elements-EmilyHenderson"},{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/normal/cre-d12-rec13-01822.webp?sfvrsn=ef64dd3e_11","ThumbnailImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/thumbnails/cre-d12-rec13-01186.webp?sfvrsn=916ff054_4","VideoUrl":null,"Title":"Canyon Ridge Elements 01"},{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/normal/cr-elements-d11-plain-long-01.webp?sfvrsn=68bbee9e_5","ThumbnailImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/thumbnails/cr-elements-d11-plain-long-01s.webp?sfvrsn=394053e2_2","VideoUrl":null,"Title":"Canyon Ridge Elements 02"},{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/normal/cr-elements-iron-orel.webp?sfvrsn=1d6b6d48_3","ThumbnailImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/canyonridgeelements/thumbnails/cr-elements-iron-ores.webp?sfvrsn=ea705aa2_1","VideoUrl":null,"Title":"Canyon Ridge Elements Iron ore"},{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/defau